name: DONKR
description:
A tribute artwork for my own Cat. His name is Donkr, today he's 10 years old. I actually didn't know when exactly he born, but I know when I took him from the street when he just 2-3 months old, lonely and meaowing :))).
He couple of times visited vet clinic, 3 times to be exact.

I always portray him as black panther or a black puma, bcoz he got big and muscular body, not a common for just a cat.
2011 feels like blink of an eye, it was 10 years ago.

I really hope, he always healthy and have a long life :)
